metadata.name: SKREAMAZ #1
metadata.description: Skreamaz are an advance being that has long surpassed humans naively antiquated way of life and now reside on a higher plane of existence. Their sole mission is to spread their teachings to the lucky few they deem worthy. Amidst a burgeoning world of decentralised currencies Skreamaz now drift, searching for suitable candidates. They are the ever present ghosts in the ETH blockchain.
